{"id":"7c759ac9-d53e-4209-bef3-79105ffd0193","name":"Muskets & Sorcery - RP","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\"Coal, copper, and the Aether.\" London.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZPi6pyqmgB2mZoDeHGD9i.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 20, 20);\">.</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 20, 20);\">.</span></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 200, 220);\">◈─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 230);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 238);\">◈</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 210, 225);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 240, 248);\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 210, 225);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 200, 220);\"><strong>We</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 213, 230);\"><strong>lco</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 226, 238);\"><strong>me </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 235, 243);\"><strong>to </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 226, 238);\"><strong>Ae</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 213, 230);\"><strong>th</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 200, 220);\"><strong>eria</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 210, 225);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 240, 248);\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 200, 220);\"> ◈</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 230);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 200, 220);\">─◈</span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 20, 20);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 235, 243);\">The year is <strong>1890</strong>. The British Empire stands at the height of its power — and magic has never been more ordinary, or more dangerous.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 238);\">This is not a world of chosen ones and prophecies. <strong>Aetheria</strong> is a world where magic is a measurable force, industrialized and commodified, taught in schools, burned in engines, and fired from the barrels of spell-etched muskets. The ancient and the modern do not merely coexist — they are inseparable.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 230);\">London breathes coal smoke and Aetheric discharge in equal measure. Factory-covens run day and night. Battle-mages drill on Woolwich Common. A Sorcerer born in the East End has more in common with a dockworker than with a lord — and yet doors open for them that never would otherwise.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 205, 223);\">And <strong><u>YOU</u></strong> are someone in this world. What that means is yours to decide.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 20, 20);\">.</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 20, 20);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/58L3n7mNMZFQwji7jqj0R.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 20, 20);\">.</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 20, 20);\">.</span></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 185, 215);\">◈─◈─◈ | </span><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 192, 220);\"><strong>Fe</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 202, 226);\"><strong>atu</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 215, 233);\"><strong>res</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 185, 215);\"> | ◈─◈─◈</span></h1><p><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 20, 20);\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 195, 220);\">◈ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 225, 238);\">Victorian-era magical world with full internal consistency — no chosen ones, no prophecy, just a world that works and people living inside it</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 195, 220);\">◈ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 215, 232);\">Five-tier <strong>Aetheric Proficiency system</strong> — every character has a defined magical level from Ambient to Exceptional, giving instant context without a stat sheet</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(238, ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"HeF-XqI4ScQr4CcTi79gz.webp","creator":"ManPL","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","🔮 Magical","👭 Multiple","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG"],"chats":36,"messages":825,"created_at":"2026-05-27T13:03:27.840226+00:00"}